	<div class="post"><h2>Home Page for the former <i>Velvet Elvis</i></h2>
   <div class="entrytext">


	<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="right">
	  <tr >
	    <td rowspan="2" colspan="2"><p>The <i>Velvet Elvis</i> is a 1998 Rhodes 22 manufactured by <a href="http://rhodes22.com" target="_blank">General Boats</a>.  She spent her first few years as a demo boat, going to boat shows and being sailed by her loving manufacturers.</p>

	        <p>In 2000, General Boats decided to let her go to the poor youngish sailers in Louisiana who were buying on credit and couldn't afford an entirely new boat.  Within a day, she had damage.  Within a month, she had a name.</p></td>
	    <td width=250 align="right"><img src="/img/velvetelvis.jpg" width=250 aborder=0 vspace=4></td>
	  </tr>
