	    <td width="100%" colspan ="3">
			<p>We sail <i>Velvet Elvis</i> on Lake Ponchartrain, which has some advantages.  There are a number of good destinations for an overnight trip, but the lake is so big, that each one requires a full weekend commitment.  Most trips (and some daysails) include a minor fiasco or two that might make for a good story now and then.</p>
